<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation to Join QnAFlowAI</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; background-color: #f2f3f8; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <div
        style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); padding: 20px;">

        <!-- Logo Section -->
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <img src="https://yourwebsite.com/logo.png" alt="Platform Logo" style="max-width: 150px;">
        </div>

        <!-- Invitation Content -->
        <h1 style="color: #1e1e2d; font-size: 24px; margin: 0; text-align: center;">Password Change Request
        </h1>
        <p style="color: #455056; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;">
            Hello <%= name %>,
        </p>

        <p style="color: #455056; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;">
            You have submitted a password change request.
        </p>

        <p style="color: #455056; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;">
            If it wasn't you please disregard this email and make sure you can still login to your account. If it was
            you, then confirm the password change and <a href="<%= resetPasswordUrl %>">click here</a>
        </p>

        <p style="color: #455056; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;">
            Thank you
        </p>


        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74); line-height: 18px; text-align: center;">
            Â© <strong>
                <%=year%> qaflowai.com
            </strong>
        </p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>